{"id":232812588,"title":"分享＃幫助長期記憶的計畫產生器","content":"嗨各位，這是我在語文版的首Po\n\n無意間看到一位 Youtuber 分享 有效率的達成長期記憶 的方法，就在網路上找了一下製作這種計劃表的網站發現都只找的到簡體字的版本，規則上也大同小異。\n\n由於都沒有找到繁體字的版本，所以乾脆花點時間做一個產生器給台灣的學生使用，介面也稍微比較友善一點XD。\n\n可以先看一下這位 Youtuber 分享的影片。\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zbu9WBAZCZE\n\n簡單來說就是透過長時間且有規律的複習來達到長期記憶的效果。\n\n本網站的計畫表的複習規則為背完單字的第 1 , 2 , 6 , 8 , 15, 26 天進行複習。\n\n生成計畫表後，分別在要看的單字卡 ( 或是你正在學的任何東西 ) 上做上 list + number 的記號，就可以依照計劃表進行複習了。\n\n也有提供簡易的儲存及載入功能，可以幫助你記錄不同的計畫表，需要的時候再根據計畫表名稱到載入記錄到頁面。\n\n\n\n希望可以幫助到正在奮鬥的你們。\n\nhttps://milletbard.com/26Memory\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/Th4pQGn.png","excerpt":"嗨各位，這是我在語文版的首Po，無意間看到一位 Youtuber 分享 有效率的達成長期記憶 的方法，就在網路上找了一下製作這種計劃表的網站發現都只找的到簡體字的版本，規則上也大同小異。由於都沒有找到","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-02T14:09:20.308Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T14:21:46.674Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":53,"tags":[],"topics":["英文","日語","TOEIC","韓文"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"朝陽科技大學","department":"資訊工程系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":53}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Th4pQGn.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"de7ba682-7b9c-4b5b-882c-87d0fe6ca990","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/zbu9WBAZCZE/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/zbu9WBAZCZE/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/zbu9WBAZCZE/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-02T14:21:46.674Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-02T14:21:46.674Z"},{"id":"de7ba682-7b9c-4b5b-882c-87d0fe6ca990","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zbu9WBAZCZE","normalizedUrl":"ht